\n<Luna>As you can see if you would look around there's Statues and Demons blocking your way to select area's of the Spawns. Your friend's are more than likely in another area. Statues require specific duties to be done to be removed and you need to have enough Statues removed, enough Humclovers and a high enough level to defeat Demons.
\<Luna>You'll need to complete taksks, tasks need to be complete and some have retrictions. There are different types of tasks like Minigames, Quizzes, Battles, Events, Etc...

How do I find more tasks?

\n<Luna>Tasks are scattered throughout my playground, some are easier to spot than others. Some require other tasks or other requirements before appearing. Explore more, some tasks are hidden. Try checking behind things like trees or complete currently available tasks,
How do I get past the statues?

\n<Luna>Statues need specific requirements to get by them. Read what the statues say carefully to understand what you need to do. There are cases were some statues "don't work" or are "restricted" in this case the statue will stay it's unavailable.
What exactly should I be doing?
\n<Luna>Right now, complete tasks, gain levels and collect Humclovers.

\n<Luna>Lacking in resources and equipment? Enemies drop various thing try killing some monsters or you could complete task and get rewarded. Exploring around is key as well. There doesn't seem to be any shops around here... maybe some people could open some.
